  "instructions": [
    "Heat the sesame oil in a large saucepan over medium heat.",
    "Add the ginger and cook for 2 minutes, stirring occasionally.",
    "Pour in the vegetable broth and bring to a boil.",
    "Reduce heat to low and simmer for 10 minutes.",
    "In a small bowl, whisk together the coconut cream and brown sugar until smooth.",
    "Add the coconut cream mixture to the saucepan and stir to combine.",
    "Cook for an additional 2 minutes, or until the sauce has thickened slightly.",
    "Add the rice noodles to the saucepan and cook for 2-3 minutes, or until tender.",
    "Stir in the cilantro, lime juice, salt, and black pepper.",
    "Serve the noodles hot, garnished with crushed peanuts and scallions.",
    "Garnish with additional cilantro and scallions, if desired."
  ],
